chapter 1 "Introduction"

                 A Short History of Wyr and Surrounding Environs

                            Quilled by Balfor Zigil

   Yes...it is the year ONE in Wyr as decided by The Council of Eight in 
their esteemable wisdom to create the Cyclical Calendar. Each month signifies
a name from one of the "great" families - each a member of the Council. Great
ego's aside, the continent of Etnar is far older than the new calendar indicates.

